data.description: Price Reduced!! Quintessential farmhouse just blocks from downtown St. Charles, shopping, restaurants, parks and Fox River Access! Warm and inviting front porch overlooking your neighborhood! Well maintained, features original woodwork, built-in China cabinet in dining room, hardwood floors at entry leading to kitchen. Huge rear yard offers plenty of space to gather! Oversized detached two car garage offers additional space for hobbyists or storage. Additional parking pad adjacent to front of house. Updates include plumbing (2018), furnace and central air serviced (2017), roof (2016). Fully functional basement with rough-in for bathroom ready to go! The bathroom is located on the first floor, and bedrooms are upstairs.
